metadata.name: Duality
metadata.description:
Edition 1 of 1

3511 x 5000px, JPG
Photographed using a NIKON D850 with a TAMRON SP 24-70mm F2.8 lens.
The physical artwork is 450 x 640 mm (17,7 x 25,2 in), it is made with four different inks and two pens on a yupo paper.

This artwork was created using a custom hand built drawing machine. I create each piece by carefully adjusting the speed of three motors and other settings. Each piece is unique.

The physical artwork will be sent to the first buyer of the NFT.
